::Hot Rod/Prowl::

They saw where the rocks were coming from.
"Hot Rod, the honor is yours," says Prowl.

"You got it," replys Hot Rod.
He locks onto the covor that ?????? was behind, and shot three laser
blasts that way. However these were more warning shots then an attack.
